query:
INSERT INTO static.stop (id, name, geom, data)
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::INTEGER[],
                $2::TEXT[],
                $3::GEOMETRY[],
                $4::JSONB[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                name = EXCLUDED.name,
                geom = EXCLUDED.geom,
                data = EXCLUDED.data
